{"lastModified":1762772704965,"uri":"c::10317073198::vessel::6d6d0020-c1b7-11ee-8ae5-af5c8fd965c1","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nDiscover a Sea of... Harmony\nIf you want pure elegance without giving up on true comfort, it’s about time to meet Oceanis 46.1. Boasting all the features of a large cruising yacht, Oceanis 46.1 combines them with a rare balance between stylish design, usable space and performance. Her stepped hull opens up an impressive amount of space inside. Still her seakeeping performance is unparalleled.\n\nEasy to sail, easy-going and fast, the Oceanis 46.1 can be customized to make her unique, appealing to any crew and to your very special demands. Attention to design details makes life on board a real pleasure. Sail confidently and enjoy your vacation, knowing that you are always safe with her.","blueprint":{"name":"ETHEREAL","images":["/media/media::image::c::10317073198::vessel::6d6d0020-c1b7-11ee-8ae5-af5c8fd965c1::assets::f1410380-c1e7-11ee-a6ad-47466fc6912c.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10317073198::vessel::6d6d0020-c1b7-11ee-8ae5-af5c8fd965c1::assets::f8de2be0-c1e7-11ee-a6ad-47466fc6912c.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10317073198::vessel::6d6d0020-c1b7-11ee-8ae5-af5c8fd965c1::assets::2b9320e0-c1e8-11ee-a6ad-47466fc6912c.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10317073198::vessel::6d6d0020-c1b7-11ee-8ae5-af5c8fd965c1::assets::f8ddb6b0-c1e7-11ee-a6ad-47466fc6912c.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10317073198::vessel::6d6d0020-c1b7-11ee-8ae5-af5c8fd965c1::assets::f8de7a00-c1e7-11ee-a6ad-47466fc6912c.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10317073198::vessel::6d6d0020-c1b7-11ee-8ae5-af5c8fd965c1::assets::f8dec820-c1e7-11ee-a6ad-47466fc6912c.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10317073198::vessel::6d6d0020-c1b7-11ee-8ae5-af5c8fd965c1::assets::f8df3d50-c1e7-11ee-a6ad-47466fc6912c.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10317073198::vessel::6d